          {
            "text": {
              "status": "generated",
              "div": "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><h3>Annotation</h3><table class=\"hl7__eu__lab__report\"><tr><th>Conclusion and Recommendations based on this report and previous findings known to us</th></tr><tr><td>The patient shows mild normocytic, normochromic anemia (low hemoglobin and hematocrit) with normal leukocyte and platelet counts. Platelet distribution width is elevated, suggesting increased platelet size variability, which may indicate reactive or regenerative changes. No acute cytopenias or leukocytosis are present. Correlation with clinical context and further evaluation of anemia etiology is recommended.</td></tr></table></div>"
